# COMET 30: 5S Intelligent Power Management & Telemetry System
Custom 5-Cell Lithium Platform featuring a Deterministic Protection Matrix and Deterministic Out-of-Band Telemetry

![KiCad](https://img.shields.io/badge/KiCad-v8.0-blue?logo=kicad&logoColor=white)
![Layer Count](https://img.shields.io/badge/Layers-4--Layer-green)
![Copper Weight](https://img.shields.io/badge/Copper-2oz-orange)
![Continuous Rating](https://img.shields.io/badge/Continuous_Current-30A-red)

The COMET 30 is a high-reliability, mixed-signal Battery Management System (BMS) architected for 5-Cell (5S) Lithium-Ion/Lithium-Polymer energy storage systems operating under high transient loads. The system implements an asynchronous, triple-redundant safety topology designed to isolate hard-wired analog fault reflexes from the high-level digital telemetry plane, ensuring structural cell safety even under catastrophic firmware or logic failures.

```mermaid
graph TD
    subgraph Battery Pack (5S Li-Po)
        CELLS[Cell Stack 5S]
    end

    subgraph Layer 1: Autonomous Analog Protection
        BM[BM3451 Primary AFE]
        INF[Parallel Infineon FETs]
    end

    subgraph Layer 2: Embedded Digital Telemetry
        ESP[ESP32-C3 Microcontroller]
        INA[INA226 I2C Monitor]
        ADS[Dual ADS1115 ADCs]
    end

    subgraph Layer 3: Irreversible Active Failsafe
        BQ[BQ771807 Secondary Overvoltage Monitor]
        SFK[Dexerials SFK-2045 Chemical Fuse]
    end

    CELLS --> BM
    CELLS --> BQ
    CELLS --> INA
    CELLS --> ADS
    
    BM -->|Gate Control| INF
    ESP -->|I2C Telemetry| INA
    ESP -->|I2C Per-Cell| ADS
    
    ESP -->|Software Override| INF
    
    BQ -->|Pyrotechnic/Heater Actuation| SFK
    ESP -->|PIN_NUKE GPIO| SFK
    SFK -->|Physical Inline Severance| CELLS
